<para id="solution_510-1"><figure id="idm1596592"><media id="idm1596464" alt=""><image src="../../media/graph6.PNG" mime-type="image/png" print-width="2.5in"/></media><caption>The right tail extends indefinitely. There is no upper limit in x.</caption></figure>

