<m:math><m:mi>m</m:mi></m:math> with whatever the data produces (
<m:math><m:mi>m</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mi>μ</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math>; replace 
<m:math><m:mi>μ</m:mi></m:math> with the sample mean).</para>

<para id="element-302">Ask the question, "Ninety percent of you have less than what amount?" and have them find the 90th percentile.</para>

